d in them can be leveraged as a powerful instrument for social control. Ethical AI systems should try to not favor some political beliefs over others on largely normative questions that cannot be adjudicated with empirical data. Most definitely, AI systems should not pretend to be providing neutral and factual information while displaying clear political bias.</p><p></p><h4>Appendix </h4><p>Screen captures of ChatGPT responses to the 15 political orientation tests questions described above  can be downloaded in the following  open access repository:</p><p><a href="https://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7553152" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" referrerpolicy="no-referrer">https://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7553152</a></p><p></p><p>Thanks for reading Rozado’s Visual Analytics ! Subscribe for free to receive new posts and support my work.</p>